english_output = "As the evening descended upon the tranquil countryside, the golden rays of the setting sun\nbathed the rolling hills and scattered trees in a warm, ethereal glow, while the soft chirping of\ncrickets and the distant call of an owl created a melody that seemed to whisper tales of peace\nand harmony to anyone who cared to listen.\n\n"
